Interface ArchetypeVolume

    public interface ArchetypeVolume

      • apply

        void apply(Location<World> location,
           BlockChangeFlag changeFlag)
        Applies this archetype at the given location. The archetype will be mapped onto the given world such that the origin on the archetype lines up with the given position.
        Parameters:
        location - The location to apply at
        changeFlag - The flag to use for toggling various operations on block placement
